---
import ProjectItem from "./Projects/ProjectItem.astro";
const futureDate = new Date();
futureDate.setFullYear(futureDate.getFullYear() + 10);

// TODO: TO BE CONFIRMED
const respondDate = new Date("2024-02-28");
const eventDate = new Date("2024-03-15");
---

<div class="-mt-6 h-12 rotate-1 border-t-8 border-accent2 bg-dark-bg"></div>

<section class="flex justify-center px-8 py-16 sm:py-32">
  <div
    class="flex max-w-3xl grow flex-col space-y-6 border-2 border-accent bg-primary-bg px-6 py-8 text-sm shadow-[16px_16px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] sm:space-y-10 sm:px-12 sm:py-8 sm:text-lg md:px-16 md:py-12"
  >
    <!-- ----------------------------- Letterhead ------------------------------ -->
    <div class="text-right text-xl leading-5 md:text-2xl md:leading-6">
      <p>
        {
          futureDate.toLocaleDateString(undefined, {
            year: "numeric",
            month: "long",
            day: "numeric",
          })
        }
      </p>
      <p>
        {Math.round((respondDate.valueOf() - Date.now()) / (24 * 60 * 60 * 1000))} days to
        respond
      </p>
      <p>
        {Math.round((eventDate.valueOf() - Date.now()) / (24 * 60 * 60 * 1000))} days
        until event
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- --------------------------- Letter Contents --------------------------- -->

    <div class="-mt-8 space-y-4 text-2xl leading-6 md:text-3xl md:leading-8">
      <p
        class="text-3xl italic drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_#FF5DA9] sm:pt-4 sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl"
      >
        Greetings, hacker.
      </p>
      <p>
        I hope you and your loved ones are well. It’s scary how fast the “zombie virus”
        has spread across the world.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our cities have turned to battlefields. Our subways and schools have grown
        infected with the fallen.
      </p>
      <p class="drop-shadow-[0_0_4px_#FF5DA9]">It could be the beginning of the end.</p>
      <p>
        But technology still stands. WiFi is up, electricity runs, and hardware operates.
      </p>
      <p class="italic drop-shadow-[0_0_4px_#FF5DA9]">We need your help.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- ----------------------------- Letter CTA ------------------------------ -->

    <div class="justify-center py-4 sm:py-8">
      <div
        class="flex max-w-3xl grow flex-col gap-4 text-center text-white sm:gap-6 md:gap-10"
      >
        <p class="text-3xl leading-6 sm:text-4xl sm:leading-7 md:text-5xl md:leading-9">
          Join <span class="text-accent">150 hackers</span> like you for
          <span class="text-accent2">42 hours</span> at our safehouse.
        </p>

        <p
          class="text-3xl leading-6 text-white drop-shadow-[0_0_4px_#FF5DA9] sm:text-4xl sm:leading-7 md:text-5xl md:leading-9"
        >
          Build something, <span class="italic">anything</span>, to help us survive this
          apocalypse.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
